-- Mitsubishi Tanabe Pharma Plans to Produce Drugs in India, Sankei Reports
-- B y   T a k   K u m a k u r a
-- 2010-11-10T22:02:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/mitsubishi-tanabe-pharma-plans-to-produce-drugs-in-india-sankei-reports.html
Mitsubishi Tanabe Pharma Corp. plans
to produce drugs in India, the Sankei newspaper said, citing an
interview with President Michihiro Tsuchiya. The Osaka-based
company will either build a plant in India or outsource
production to a local company, according to the newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Takehiko Kumakura at 
 tkumakura@bloomberg.net  